<section style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px; background-position: 25.8037% -43.1473%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: 29.7866%; background-attachment: scroll; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/apprToXjJCE2967/image/ueditor/71671000_1524734304.png&#39;); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color:#51504f"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">如果人类想要生存并向更高层次迈进，那么一种新的思考方式非常重要。</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: right; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color:#51504f"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">——爱因斯坦</strong></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 100%; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 0.62em; height: 0.62em; float: left; background-color: rgb(255, 202, 0); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="width: 0.62em; height: 0.62em; float: right; background-color: rgb(255, 202, 0); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><section style="padding: 10px 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">什么是「阈限思维」？</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">“阈限”这个词来自拉丁文，本意是<span style="color: rgb(81, 80, 79); box-sizing: border-box;">临界点</span>。<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box;">临界点</span></strong>意味着在边界或边缘。就像是处于一个事物的边界处，或处于两个事物之间，不属于其中任何一方。比如一位老师，可以说他是这门课的一部分，却不能说他属于这门课。</p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; width: 100%; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; overflow: hidden !important; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/apprToXjJCE2967/image/ueditor/4158800_1524734305.png" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">每天你都会遇到阈限状态，只不过多数时候你不知道他们叫做“阈限状态”，比如你半睡半醒的状态，</span><strong style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">以及你在半夜或洗澡的时候突然想到一个好主意！</strong><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">跟随本书，你可以培养出一个新的思维方式，据此突破固有的思维。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">而这种体验，即被称作<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box;">“阈限思考”</span></strong>。</p></section></section></section></section><section style="width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 0.62em; height: 0.62em; float: left; background-color: rgb(255, 202, 0); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="width: 0.62em; height: 0.62em; float: right; background-color: rgb(255, 202, 0); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 40px; height: 5px; line-height: 5px; text-align: right; margin-left: auto; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; width: 30px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(255, 202, 0); border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0); border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0); border-left-color: rgb(255, 202, 0); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="widt